{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/showsuserlocation"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"assign","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"BOOL","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"showsUserLocation","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Setting this property to ","type":"text"},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" causes the map view to use the Core Location","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"framework to find the current location. As long as this property is ","type":"text"},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"map view continues to track the user’s location and update it periodically.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This property does not indicate whether the user’s position is actually visible","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"on the map, only whether the map view is allowed to display it. To determine","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"whether the user’s position is visible, use the ","type":"text"},{"code":"userLocationVisible","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" property.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The default value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Your app must specify a value for "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSLocationWhenInUseUsageDescription"},{"type":"text","text":" or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSLocationAlwaysUsageDescription"},{"type":"text","text":" in its "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Info.plist"},{"type":"text","text":" to satisfy the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"requirements of the underlying Core Location framework when enabling this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"property.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you implement a custom location manager, set the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"locationManager"},{"type":"text","text":" before"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"calling "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"showsUserLocation"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"property","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"showsUserLocation"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)showsUserLocation","roleHeading":"Instance Property","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"title":"showsUserLocation","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"showsUserLocation"}],"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L590","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"}},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/showsUserLocation"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A Boolean value indicating whether the map may display the user location."}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","te